description:
Yagami Natsumi stars in the "Cosprayers" show as Miko Rayer (Hoshino Koto). She is 17 years of age and is under the belief that she was only enlisted for her looks and that her acting is of poor quality.
Her name is derived from Yagami Youko (八神洋子) of Gekisou Sentai Car Rangers (激走戦隊カーレンジャー) and Shinohara Natsumi (志乃原菜摘) of Car Rangers (カーレンジャー)
name: Yagami Natsumi
